                        	<a href="/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=147&Itemid=78"><img width="50" height="50" src="/images/stories/eventimages/ream12_web.jpg" alt="Horizon 2020 and the future of European research" title="Horizon 2020 and the future of European research" /></a>
