                            <p class="date">Thursday, 21st June 2012<br />International Auditorium, Brussels</p>
                            <p>After years of anticipation, the Commission’s proposal for Horizon 2020, the follow-up to Framework 7, is finally out. This document will define the direction, scope and financing of research in Europe for the next decade. <a href="/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=147&Itemid=78">Read more</a></p>
